SAY @,,1 Ah! It feels good to be working again!
TIMERF 1,SetCustomVendorOwner <SRC>
IF (<TAG0.Rent.End>)
 SRC.TAG0.VENDORS.RENT ++
ELSE
 SRC.TAG0.VENDORS ++
ENDIF

